CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 28, 1956, pg. 16, reads: "Congratulations - Mr. and Mrs. Henry Price (left) receive congratulations from Mr. and Mrs. W. M. Haughery and tiny W. M. Haughery III at the reception which followed their wedding at Canaan Baptist Church. The bride is the former Josie Dae Pass. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of wedding party with five men, including groom Henry Price, and five women, including bride Josie Dae Pass Price wearing light colored hat and light colored sheer elbow length fingerless gloves, posed in interior with wainscoting and landscape mural, another version
